  <title>What does it do?</title>
  <para>This extension is intended to generate all sorts of lists. The data sources for the list can be a database or an extbase repository or anything you write a data-backend for (SOAP, CSV, XML, ...). </para>
  <para>There are different steps you have to do if you want to set up a list. For a detailed example see section &quot;Instruction&quot; ###TODO insert link here###.</para>
